column2: SELECT u.up_col0 as [col0], # + cast (x.objId as varchar (#) ) + #+ cast (x.objId as varchar (#) ) + # as objID, p.ra, p.dec, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, p.rest_ug, p.rest_gr FROM #x x, #upload u, Photoz AS p JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS s ON s.objID = p.objID WHERE u.up_id = x.up_id and x.objID = p.objID ORDER BY x.up_id
